Kraft Doesn’t Rule Out U.K. Job Cuts After March 2012, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-03-16T01:58:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/kraft-doesn-t-rule-out-u-k-job-cuts-after-march-2012-ft-says.html
  Kraft Foods Inc. (KFT)  Corporate Affairs
and Legal Director Marc Firestone told U.K. lawmakers the U.S.
food company couldn’t rule out job cuts at its British plants
after March 2012, the Financial Times reported, citing testimony
at a parliamentary select committee hearing into the company’s
takeover of Cadbury Plc.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 